thread.title_full: TAXIBOX mobile self-storage reviewed by Joan

author: Joan
title: Joan
text: Taxibox were very prompt and helpful at every stage of their service. They provided accurate information to assist in decision making about the number of boxes required. I appreciated the timely phone calls when the boxes were either being delivered or collected. Would recommend to others.
